To install the dependencies of Project Chaplin, you will need to install the
following packages:

An AMQP server like RabbitMQ (change config/servers.ini - section "amqp" to set credentials)
Apache + PHP
MySQL
FFMPEG/AVConv

For simple SQL setup create the user and database:
mysql -uroot -p < sql/createuser.sql
[enter mysql root password]

mysql -uchaplin -pchaplin chaplin < sql/schema.sql

To run the broadcast nodejs server:
nodejs node/server.js

To run the processor for processing uploads:
php cli/cli.php cli encode

To run the processor for importing YouTube:
php cli/cli.php cli youtube
